    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained with an obsessive attention to detail that is evident from the moment you approach it. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish completely free of stone chips or swirl marks, complemented by pristine, uncurbed alloy wheels. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and taut, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma, while every technological feature and button operates with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio and housed in a climate-controlled garage its entire life. This is not just a pre-owned car; it is a showroom-quality specimen for the discerning buyer who demands perfection in every stitch and seal.",
      "price": 48500.0,
